response.overview: REBD-674: The starring of this work is Rena Miyashita! - ! - A cute 20-year-old beautiful girl with a slender style with big bright eyes! - ! - Her hobbies are sleeping, her favorite food is sushi, she likes horror movies and she is a cat-like girl who likes her own pace. - With a height of over 160 centimeters and slender and long limbs, she is a high-quality model with a striking image. - Contrary to her easy-going appearance, she has excellent motor nerves, and even after her sports shoot was over, she was jumping rope and surprised the staff by successfully double jumping behind her. - She talks casually with the crew during breaks in the filming, but when the camera turns around in the interview scene, she gets nervous and stiff for some reason, which makes me smile. - I would like you to share her happy memories and records that Rena-chan, who is cute and slightly whimsical, spins! - !
